Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhone kaha tha — kitchen mein mat aana. Aaj main apni kitchen ki queen hoon.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.30,0:00:08.38,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Kitchen mein mat aana... 🍳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaadi ke baad jab main sasural aayi, sapne the hazaaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lekin saas ne pehle din hi clear kar diya — yeh kitchen mera hai, tum mat aana.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.45,0:00:25.53,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Yeh kitchen MERA hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Raat ko akele room mein phone pe recipes dekhti thi. Aankhen bheegi, par hausla pakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chupke chupke tiffin banana shuru kiya. Pehle 5 customers, phir 50.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.61,0:00:42.68,Overlay,,0,0,0,,5 customers... phir 50 🔥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ek saal mein mera catering business lakhon ka ho gaya. Sab kehte the — Priya ka khaana magic hai.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.18,0:00:51.26,Overlay,,0,0,0,,PRIYA'S KITCHEN 👑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Phir woh din aaya. Saas mere restaurant ke bahar khadi thi. Ghar ka paisa khatam ho gaya tha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maine unka haath pakda aur kaha — Aaiye, ab yeh kitchen humara hai. Kuch darvaze band hote hain taake hum apna ghar bana sakein.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.34,0:01:08.42,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Ab yeh kitchen HUMARA hai. ❤️
